Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3a&H5F&\fad(671,2052)\t(3457,5660,\bord10)\pos(268.843,316)}First Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:25.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Machida Matrimonial Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've stopped caring about the changing of the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.53,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.07,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Shirasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.65,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Last stop, Wakase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:19.16,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait for the express train, it will come after...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:30.29,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,How much meaning is there to the fact that it is spring right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:59.61,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's someone else I've fallen in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:04.13,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.97,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Tsubana. Tsubana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:46.77,Dialogue - Alt,,0,0,0,,Please wait until the train comes to a complete stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, student!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I'm so out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I have about the next arranged marriage party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any particular questions, then I would like to end the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This party is restricted to members in their late 20's to early 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, someday I hope to bring down the membership age to include teens,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have a party restricted to women in their teens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't a new restaurant open up in Kanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sorting the membership data files in the back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That face... that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't show that to customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should definitely be a demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From experience, men my age can only meet teenage girls in an unlawful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's "your" demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any opportunities to meet a female high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ho...me...{Or just use "tadaima" if you feel like being extra weeaboo, most people know it by now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're going to be living with Nanoka starting tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show you Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes I do... I do, but I don't remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a freshman in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's 15 years old. She is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone commutes from far away nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can cut her commute time from two hours to one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural that we let her stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got dumped by your lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't intend on getting back together with mom, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a family member!{Or just "She's family!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.29,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,With my carefree life living with Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:31.82,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I have a mother and a sister who's 12 years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please introduce her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?{What the hell are you thinking?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you hiding something so important from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's basically like I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents got divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met my mom, who took custody of her, a couple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I haven't seen my sister at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of partner are you interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I came while you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my lunch break anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to get the keys to my place{room} back.{More like place, "Heya" is often used to refer to apartments/etc as well as individual rooms}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be better during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really letting me go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just accepted things so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is all I meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, have you ever loved anyone from the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:13.41,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Then what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the party, we're planning to have three events,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if we could divide the food and have it brought out to match the timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, concerning the audio equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. There are for the place next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.  Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:48.25,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What do I say to a woman that says she has another man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a place that kind of hurts for a bachelor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cool about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what she dislikes about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try inviting that girl you broke up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you guys will get back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's going to get back together with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad. {Or maybe "Thank goodness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asking out high school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm interrupting your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is good. I was waiting to meet a someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I came too early and I needed to kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meeting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. What would you like to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be boring with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received it during my junior high graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from the person I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't his second button.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.61,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}In Japan it is traditional upon graduating to give the second button from your school uniform to a girl you like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I liked him since I was a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's really handsome or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gathered up all my courage and confessed to him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he's going out with a junior at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the window could open, I could throw it out from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still like him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then don't say that you're going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has someone that he's going out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We go to different{separate} high schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll never even see each other anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you love someone so straightforward and honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got dumped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's really different from your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My feelings totally cooled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:18:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really know if I really loved her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should definitely treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the feelings that you have inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I got rejected, I kept walking with my head down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I didn't notice the flowers blooming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you stopped me back at the train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The petals were falling like snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and for a moment I couldn't tell where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.22,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's the same for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:14.52,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Where is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.37,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,this place that I've always been at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.65,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is being here unforgivable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here too, Koshiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since you siblings have gotten together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you two recognize each other right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with the two of you? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we have for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother? {Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little sister.
