Comment: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A girl that I got dumped by came to my office, so I was kind of apprehensive.
Comment: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went on a date with my younger sister without knowing.
Comment: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cried in front of a high school student at my age.
Comment: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this all right?!
Comment: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your punishment is Sumaki Nagashi!
